This package relies on the https://github.com/lz4/lz4 package.
Be sure to download and make the library.

It optionally also depends on libz for gzip compression.
This comes automatically with MacOS and may be obtained for Linux as well.

The evio library also depends on the Disruptor library:
https://github.com/Abc-Arbitrage/Disruptor-cpp.git

This repository has been added to, and so, use the one provide by CODA
and not the one obtained directly from github.

(The original Disruptor library was written in Java:
 https://github.com/LMAX-Exchange/disruptor.git)


It depends on boost threads as well as .........